beer.beer_description:
The sacrificial campfires were lit and waves of soft, creamy marshmallows were toasted to crispy perfection to harness the rich, sticky sweetness we needed for this juicy beer! Bursting with heady aromas of citrus peel, peach, mango, lime and orange blossom with gooey, melted notes of caramel and vanilla with a dusting of biscuit crumbs to pull you ever closer towards s’mores territory…Drink at dusk!
DRINK FRESH - STAY RAD

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 30 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 7!
